 Status is achieved in the process of the consumer’s maximisation of her
 projected assets-accumulation using the incomes received from the variety
 of income strata she may belong to in the future (due to transitions through
 the income bands).
 While status consumption is the cost to participate in a tiered rewards
 game towards the universal race to exclusivity, it does not mean that status
